import{_ as e,o as r,c as o,b as t}from"./app-a6eacc5a.js";const a={},d=t('<h1 id="hard-drive" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#hard-drive" aria-hidden="true">#</a> hard drive</h1><p>A computer hard drive is an electronic device that stores and <code>retrieves</code> data. It is one of the most important components of a computer, as it provides the storage space for all the files and programs that are installed on the computer.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p>计算机硬盘是一种电子设备，用于存储和检索数据。它是计算机最重要的组件之一，因为它为安装在计算机上的文件和程序提供存储空间。</p></details><details class="custom-container details"><summary>words</summary><p>retrieve<br><code>美: [rɪˈtriv] 英: [rɪˈtriːv]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 取回；(猎狗将猎获物)找回；拉回(钩鱼线)；拯救<br> n. 挽回</p></blockquote></details><p>There are two types of hard drives: traditional hard drives and <code>solid-state</code> drives (SSDs). Traditional hard drives use spinning disks to store data, while SSDs use <code>flash</code> memory to do the same thing. Traditional hard drives are larger and slower than SSDs, but they are more <code>affordable</code> and still <code>widely</code> used today.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p>有两类硬盘：传统硬盘和固态硬盘(SSD)。传统硬盘使用旋转磁盘来存储数据，而SSD则使用闪存存储器来实现相同的功能。传统硬盘比SSD大且慢，但它们更便宜，并且今天仍然被广泛使用。</p></details><details class="custom-container details"><summary>words</summary><p>solid-state<br><code>英 [ˌsɒlɪd ˈsteɪt]美 [ˌsɑːlɪd ˈsteɪt]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 固态的；固态电子学的；固态物理学的；使用电晶体的</p></blockquote><p>flash<br><code>美: [flæʃ] 英: [flæʃ]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 闪光；闪光灯；闪耀；（尤指信号灯）闪亮<br> v. 闪光；掠过；（向…）用光发出（信号）；显示<br> adj. 庞大的；昂贵的；穿着奢华的<br> 网络 闪存；动画；快闪记忆体</p></blockquote><p>affordable<br><code>美: [əˈfɒrdəb(ə)l] 英: [əˈfɔː(r)dəb(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 负担得起的<br> 网络 实惠；负担的起的；买得起的</p></blockquote><p>widely<br><code>美: [ˈwaɪdli] 英: [&#39;waɪdli]</code></p><blockquote><p>adv. 广泛地；普遍地；大量地；很大程度上<br> 网络 广泛的；大大地</p></blockquote></details><p>When a user opens a file or program on their computer, the operating system (OS) sends a request to the hard drive&#39;s controller unit (CU). The CU then reads the requested data from the <code>appropriate</code> <code>sector</code> on the hard drive and sends it to the CPU. The CPU then processes the data and returns control to the OS.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p>当用户在计算机上打开文件或程序时，操作系统(OS)会向硬盘控制器单元(CU)发送请求。然后CU从硬盘的适当扇区读取所请求的数据并将其发送到CPU。CPU然后处理数据并将控制权返回给OS。</p></details><details class="custom-container details"><summary>words</summary><p>appropriate<br><code>美: [əˈproʊpriˌeɪt] 英: [əˈprəʊpriˌeɪt]</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 拨款；剽窃；挪用；〈正式〉非法占有<br> adj. 恰当的<br> 网络 适当的；合适的；适合的</p></blockquote><p>sector<br><code>美: [ˈsektər] 英: [ˈsektə(r)]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 行业；扇形；（尤指军事管制的）区域<br> 网络 扇区；部门；磁区</p></blockquote></details><p>Hard drives can become <code>corrupted</code> or fail over time, which can cause serious problems for your computer. To avoid this, it is important to back up your important files regularly and to keep your operating system and <code>antivirus</code> software up to date. <code>Additionally</code>, using an <code>external</code> hard drive or cloud storage service can provide an additional <code>layer</code> of protection for your data.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p>硬盘可能会因时间而变得损坏或失效，这可能会对您的计算机造成严重问题。为了避免这种情况，定期备份您的重要文件非常重要，并且要保持您的操作系统和杀毒软件更新。此外，使用外部硬盘驱动器或云存储服务可以为您的数据提供另一层保护。</p></details><details class="custom-container details"><summary>words</summary><p>corrupt<br><code>美: [kəˈrʌpt] 英: [kə&#39;rʌpt]</code><br> v. 使腐败；使堕落；行贿收买；败坏(风俗等)<br> adj. 腐败的；堕落的；贪污的(官吏等)；不可靠的<br> 网络 腐化；损坏；毁坏的</p><p>antivirus<br><code>美: [ˈæntiˌvaɪrəs] 英: [&#39;ænti.vaɪrəs]</code><br> adj. 防病毒的；杀毒的<br> n. 【自】(电子计算机的)抗病毒疫苗软件<br> 网络 杀毒软件；防毒；反病毒</p><p>additionally<br><code>美: [əˈdɪʃ(ə)nəli] 英: [ə&#39;dɪʃ(ə)nəli]</code><br> adv. 另外<br> 网络 又；此外；加之</p><p>external<br><code>美: [ɪkˈstɜrn(ə)l] 英: [ɪkˈstɜː(r)n(ə)l]</code><br> n. 外部；外观；形式；外部情况<br> adj. 外部的；外面的；外界的；外来的<br> 网络 外在的；表面的；客观的</p><p>layer<br><code>美: [ˈleɪr] 英: [ˈleɪə(r)]</code><br> n. 层；层次；表层；阶层<br> v. 把…分层堆放<br> 网络 图层；图层操作；一层</p></details>',13),s=[d];function i(c,l){return r(),o("div",null,s)}const p=e(a,[["render",i],["__file","05-hard-drive.html.vue"]]);export{p as default};
